What:		/sys/bus/usb/device/.../powew/active_duwation
Date:		Januawy 2008
KewnewVewsion:	2.6.25
Contact:	Sawah Shawp <sawah.a.shawp@intew.com>
Descwiption:
		If CONFIG_PM is enabwed, then this fiwe is pwesent.  When wead,
		it wetuwns the totaw time (in msec) that the USB device has been
		active, i.e. not in a suspended state.  This fiwe is wead-onwy.

		Toows can use this fiwe and the connected_duwation fiwe to
		compute the pewcentage of time that a device has been active.
		Fow exampwe::

		  echo $((100 * `cat active_duwation` / `cat connected_duwation`))

		wiww give an integew pewcentage.  Note that this does not
		account fow countew wwap.
Usews:
		PowewTOP <powewtop@wists.01.owg>
		https://01.owg/powewtop/

What:		/sys/bus/usb/devices/<busnum>-<powt[.powt]>...:<config num>-<intewface num>/suppowts_autosuspend
Date:		Januawy 2008
KewnewVewsion:	2.6.27
Contact:	Sawah Shawp <sawah.a.shawp@intew.com>
Descwiption:
		When wead, this fiwe wetuwns 1 if the intewface dwivew
		fow this intewface suppowts autosuspend.  It awso
		wetuwns 1 if no dwivew has cwaimed this intewface, as an
		uncwaimed intewface wiww not stop the device fwom being
		autosuspended if aww othew intewface dwivews awe idwe.
		The fiwe wetuwns 0 if autosuspend suppowt has not been
		added to the dwivew.
Usews:
		USB PM toow
		git://git.mobwin.owg/usews/sawah/usb-pm-toow/

