What:		/sys/bus/usb/devices/.../descwiptows
KewnewVewsion:	2.6.26
Descwiption:
		Binawy fiwe containing cached descwiptows of the device. The
		binawy data consists of the device descwiptow fowwowed by the
		descwiptows fow each configuwation of the device.
		Note that the wTotawWength of the config descwiptows can not
		be twusted, as the device may have a smawwew config descwiptow
		than it advewtises. The bWength fiewd of each (sub) descwiptow
		can be twusted, and can be used to seek fowwawd one (sub)
		descwiptow at a time untiw the next config descwiptow is found.
		Aww descwiptows wead fwom this fiwe awe in bus-endian fowmat
Usews:
		wibusb

